http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/tamil-nadu/Man-run-over-by-train/article14619894.ece

A man crossing a railway track near here was run over by train on Thursday.Puguazhendhi (27) of Paniyur village was a mini cargo carrier driver and was about to get married in a few days.He was distributing invitations for his marriage in Enthal village.He crossed the railway track without noticing the oncoming Katpadi-Villupuram passenger train.Villupuram railway police rushed to the spot and investigation is on.